com.baypackets.ase.sbb
Class SBBEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.baypackets.ase.sbb.SBBEvent
public class SBBEvent
extends java.lang.Object

The SBBEvent class defines events generated by the SBBs to indicate the completion or failure of a specific task or operation that the application has requested from the SBB.

SBBs also notify the application when receiving SIP messages from endpoints passing the decision to the application.
